::Fenox::

Fenox smiles, patting D's shoulder. "Training rooms are good. Here, 
follow me."

She walks off toward the training rooms, looking back to make sure 
that D was following.

> 
> * D didn't mean to make Fenox lose her balence, his muscles jerking 
under 
> his fur to try and see if he could catch her but she never fell.
> D pressed his ears to his head.*
> 
> " Sorry."
> 
> * He cocked an ear in her direction then and listened to her.
> So, he could either pick to go to the training rooms or the labs. 
Well, 
> there was no contest there. D doubted that he wanted to see a lab 
again, but 
> even while he lived with the Flesh he enjoyed his sessions in the 
holo

before.*
